\begin_layout Standard
problem.
 the exponential function 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp(x)$
\end_inset

 satisfies 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp(0)=1$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp'(x)=\exp(x)$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
